OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FForced meter installations 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto be banned for over-85s  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The forcible instalment of prepayment  
OL,6, energy meters in homes of customers    
OL,7, over 85 will be banned under new rules 
OL,8, from the regulator Ofgem.              
OL,10,FSuppliers will also have to give       
OL,11,Fcustomers more chances to clear their  
OL,12,Fdebts before making them switch.       
OL,14,FIt comes after debt agents for British 
OL,15,FGas broke into some people's homes to  
OL,16,Ffit meters, sparking an outcry.        
OL,18,FBut campaigners said the new rules did 
OL,19,Fnot go far enough and vulnerable people
OL,20,Fcould still face forced installations. 
